<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="x-apple-disable-message-reformatting" />
    <title>Te avisaremos cuando esté disponible – Motomundi</title>
    <!--[if mso]>
    <noscript>
        <xml>
            <o:OfficeDocumentSettings>
                <o:PixelsPerInch>96</o:PixelsPerInch>
            </o:OfficeDocumentSettings>
        </xml>
    </noscript>
    <![endif]-->
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#f2f2f0;font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;-webkit-text-size-adjust:100%;-ms-text-size-adjust:100%;">

<!-- Preheader (hidden preview text) -->
<div style="display:none;max-height:0;overflow:hidden;mso-hide:all;">
    ¡Lo tenemos! En cuanto vuelva a estar disponible, serás el primero en saberlo. &zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;
</div>

<!-- Outer wrapper -->
<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="background-color:#f2f2f0;">
    <tr>
        <td align="center" style="padding:40px 16px;">

            <!-- Email card -->
            <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="max-width:560px;">

                <!-- ── TOP ACCENT BAR ── -->
                <tr>
                    <td style="background-color:#d6001c;height:4px;font-size:0;line-height:0;">&nbsp;</td>
                </tr>

                <!-- ── HEADER ── -->
                <tr>
                    <td style="background-color:#1a1a1a;padding:28px 40px;">
                        <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
                            <tr>
                                <td valign="middle">
                                    <a href="<%= storeUrl %>" style="text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;">
                                        <img
                                                src="https://www.motomundi.cl/Templates/MotoMundiDesktop/content/images/logo-motomundi.png"
                                                alt="Motomundi"
                                                width="160"
                                                height="auto"
                                                style="display:block;border:0;outline:none;text-decoration:none;"
                                        />
                                    </a>
                                </td>
                                <td align="right" valign="middle">
                    <span style="font-family:'Courier New',Courier,monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#666666;">
                      AVISO DE STOCK
                    </span>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </table>
                    </td>
                </tr>

                <!-- ── HERO BLOCK ── -->
                <tr>
                    <td style="background-color:#ffffff;padding:48px 40px 36px;">

                        <!-- Bell icon (inline SVG rendered as img for mail client compat) -->
                        <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
                            <tr>
                                <td align="center" style="padding-bottom:28px;">
                                    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
                                        <tr>
                                            <td style="background-color:#fce8eb;border-radius:50%;width:72px;height:72px;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;">
                                                <!-- Bell SVG -->
                                                <img
                                                        src="https://img.icons8.com/ios/72/d6001c/appointment-reminders.png"
                                                        width="36"
                                                        height="36"
                                                        alt="Notificación"
                                                        style="display:block;margin:18px auto;"
                                                />
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                    </table>
                                </td>
                            </tr>

                            <!-- Headline -->
                            <tr>
                                <td align="center" style="padding-bottom:16px;">
                                    <h1 style="margin:0;font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:26px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.25;color:#1a1a1a;letter-spacing:-0.5px;">
                                        ¡Te tenemos en lista!
                                    </h1>
                                </td>
                            </tr>

                            <!-- Subheading -->
                            <tr>
                                <td align="center" style="padding-bottom:32px;">
                                    <p style="margin:0;font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;color:#555555;max-width:400px;text-align:center;">
                                        Hemos registrado tu correo correctamente. En cuanto la talla vuelva a estar disponible, te lo haremos saber de inmediato.
                                    </p>
                                </td>
                            </tr>

                            <!-- Divider -->
                            <tr>
                                <td style="border-top:1px solid #eeeeee;padding-bottom:32px;font-size:0;line-height:0;">&nbsp;</td>
                            </tr>

                            <!-- Product summary card -->
                            <tr>
                                <td style="background-color:#fafafa;border-left:3px solid #d6001c;padding:20px 24px;">
                                    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
                                        <tr>
                                            <td>
                                                <p style="margin:0 0 4px 0;font-family:'Courier New',Courier,monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#999999;">
                                                    RESUMEN DEL AVISO
                                                </p>
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td style="padding-top:12px;">
                                                <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">

                                                    <tr>
                                                        <td style="padding-bottom:8px;">
                                                            <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
                                                                <tr>
                                                                    <td style="font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:12px;color:#999999;width:120px;">
                                                                        Correo:
                                                                    </td>
                                                                    <td style="font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:13px;color:#1a1a1a;font-weight:700;">
                                                                        <%= email %>
                                                                    </td>
                                                                </tr>
                                                            </table>
                                                        </td>
                                                    </tr>

                                                    <% if (typeof productName !== 'undefined' && productName) { %>
                                                        <tr>
                                                            <td style="padding-bottom:8px;">
                                                                <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
                                                                    <tr>
                                                                        <td style="font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:12px;color:#999999;width:120px;">
                                                                            Producto:
                                                                        </td>
                                                                        <td style="font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:13px;color:#1a1a1a;font-weight:700;">
                                                                            <%= productName %>
                                                                        </td>
                                                                    </tr>
                                                                </table>
                                                            </td>
                                                        </tr>
                                                    <% } %>

                                                    <% if (typeof size !== 'undefined' && size) { %>
                                                        <tr>
                                                            <td style="padding-bottom:8px;">
                                                                <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
                                                                    <tr>
                                                                        <td style="font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:12px;color:#999999;width:120px;">
                                                                            Talla:
                                                                        </td>
                                                                        <td>
                                      <span style="display:inline-block;background-color:#d6001c;color:#ffffff;font-family:'Courier New',Courier,monospace;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;padding:3px 10px;">
                                        <%= size %>
                                      </span>
                                                                        </td>
                                                                    </tr>
                                                                </table>
                                                            </td>
                                                        </tr>
                                                    <% } %>

                                                    <tr>
                                                        <td>
                                                            <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
                                                                <tr>
                                                                    <td style="font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:12px;color:#999999;width:120px;">
                                                                        Registrado el:
                                                                    </td>
                                                                    <td style="font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:13px;color:#1a1a1a;">
                                                                        <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString('es-ES', { day: '2-digit', month: 'long', year: 'numeric' }) %>
                                                                    </td>
                                                                </tr>
                                                            </table>
                                                        </td>
                                                    </tr>

                                                </table>
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                    </table>
                                </td>
                            </tr>

                            <!-- CTA -->
                            <tr>
                                <td align="center" style="padding-top:36px;padding-bottom:8px;">
                                    <a
                                            href="<%= storeUrl %>"
                                            style="display:inline-block;background-color:#d6001c;color:#ffffff;font-family:'Courier New',Courier,monospace;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;padding:16px 36px;"
                                    >
                                        SEGUIR COMPRANDO
                                    </a>
                                </td>
                            </tr>

                        </table>
                    </td>
                </tr>

                <!-- ── REASSURANCE STRIP ── -->
                <tr>
                    <td style="background-color:#fce8eb;padding:24px 40px;">
                        <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
                            <tr>
                                <!-- Item 1 -->
                                <td align="center" width="33%" style="padding:0 8px;">
                                    <p style="margin:0 0 4px 0;font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:18px;color:#d6001c;">✓</p>
                                    <p style="margin:0;font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:11px;color:#666666;line-height:1.5;">
                                        Aviso<br>inmediato
                                    </p>
                                </td>
                                <!-- Item 2 -->
                                <td align="center" width="33%" style="padding:0 8px;border-left:1px solid #f0b8c0;border-right:1px solid #f0b8c0;">
                                    <p style="margin:0 0 4px 0;font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:18px;color:#d6001c;">✓</p>
                                    <p style="margin:0;font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:11px;color:#666666;line-height:1.5;">
                                        Sin<br>compromiso
                                    </p>
                                </td>
                                <!-- Item 3 -->
                                <td align="center" width="33%" style="padding:0 8px;">
                                    <p style="margin:0 0 4px 0;font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:18px;color:#d6001c;">✓</p>
                                    <p style="margin:0;font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:11px;color:#666666;line-height:1.5;">
                                        Solo<br>un email
                                    </p>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </table>
                    </td>
                </tr>

                <!-- ── FOOTER ── -->
                <tr>
                    <td style="background-color:#1a1a1a;padding:28px 40px;">
                        <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
                            <tr>
                                <td align="center" style="padding-bottom:16px;">
                                    <img
                                            src="https://www.motomundi.cl/Templates/MotoMundiDesktop/content/images/logo-motomundi.png"
                                            alt="Motomundi"
                                            width="120"
                                            height="auto"
                                            style="display:block;border:0;outline:none;text-decoration:none;margin:0 auto;opacity:0.85;"
                                    />
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td align="center" style="padding-bottom:16px;">
                                    <p style="margin:0;font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:11px;color:#666666;line-height:1.6;">
                                        Has recibido este mensaje porque solicitaste un aviso de disponibilidad de stock.<br>
                                        Si no fuiste tú, puedes ignorar este correo con total tranquilidad.
                                    </p>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td align="center" style="border-top:1px solid #333333;padding-top:16px;">
                                    <p style="margin:0;font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;font-size:10px;color:#444444;line-height:1.6;">
                                        © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Motomundi SPA &nbsp;·&nbsp;
                                        <a href="<%= storeUrl %>/terminos-y-condiciones.html?open=privacy-policy" style="color:#d6001c;text-decoration:none;">Política de privacidad</a>
                                        &nbsp;·&nbsp;
                                        <a href="<%= unsubscribeUrl %>" style="color:#d6001c;text-decoration:none;">Cancelar suscripción</a>
                                    </p>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </table>
                    </td>
                </tr>

                <!-- ── BOTTOM ACCENT BAR ── -->
                <tr>
                    <td style="background-color:#d6001c;height:4px;font-size:0;line-height:0;">&nbsp;</td>
                </tr>

            </table>
            <!-- /Email card -->

        </td>
    </tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>
